[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/04/210454.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1447785","time":"2019-5-30 16:59","userId":"mp4spig","userName":"🌸九重凛🌸","userSign":"(人不抽我，我不抽人。人若抽我，我必抽人。 ...)","message":"差不多。压榨严重。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/13/291383.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1447788","time":"2019-5-30 17:04","userId":"tttbbx","userName":"雪の宿❄️","userSign":"","message":"我记得日本TV动画的集均经费天花板好像是种命的3300万日元，多数动画也就一千万出头。跟画风关系不大，原画一般是按张数算工资的，所以张数的影响更大。不过日本动画民工的廉价我觉得才是主要因素，至于为什么这么廉价，就要从历史开始说起了<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">于是进入了我的知识盲区</span>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/04/210454.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1447807","time":"2019-5-30 17:53","userId":"mp4spig","userName":"🌸九重凛🌸","userSign":"","message":"要从手冢说起了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/84/208419.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1447808","time":"2019-5-30 18:09","userId":"bruse","userName":"土豆","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九重凛</span> 说: 要从手冢说起了</q></div>等等！这么远的嘛！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/79.gif\" smileid=\"118\" alt=\"(bgm102)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/29/342917.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1447827","time":"2019-5-30 19:20","userId":"342917","userName":"某科学与不科学的超电磁炮","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九重凛</span> 说: 要从手冢说起了</q></div>手冢:一群晚辈不知变通怪我咯<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1447829","time":"2019-5-30 19:32","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av28225327\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av28225327</a><br><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/v